{
  "data": "@startuml
actor Kasir
participant "POS System" as POS
participant "Payment Gateway" as PG
participant "Database" as DB

Kasir -> POS : checkout()
POS -> PG : requestPayment(total)
PG --> POS : paymentStatus

alt Pembayaran Berhasil
  POS -> DB : simpan transaksi
  POS --> Kasir : tampilkan struk
else Pembayaran Gagal
  POS --> Kasir : tampilkan pesan gagal
end
@enduml
",
  "format": "svg"
}
